columns.name: Record ID
columns.description: An identification number assigned by DCA to record each inspection. For DCA office tracking purposes.

columns.name: Business Name
columns.description: Primary Business Name.

top.item: APPROVED OIL CO OF BROOKLYN INC
THE STOP & SHOP SUPERMARKET COMPANY LLC

columns.name: Industry
columns.description: The category that describes the business.

columns.name: Certificate Number
columns.description:
Certificate number issued to the business upon inspection. Note that there may be multiple certificate numbers for a
single inspection.

columns.name: Inspection Date
columns.description: Date when DCA conducted inspection.

columns.name: Inspection Result
columns.description: Result of inspection (e.g., No Violation Issued, Violation Issued, Pass, Fail). Refer to Appendix A for details.

columns.name: Test Type
columns.description: The test performed and the type of equipment tested. Refer to Appendix B for details.

columns.name: Approved
columns.description: The number of items that passed the inspection.

columns.name: Condemned
columns.description: The number of items that DCA condemned.

columns.name: Confiscated
columns.description: The number of items that DCA confiscated.

columns.name: Notes
columns.description:
This section is used only if the Inspection Result is “Fail” and the Test Type is “MISC FUEL OIL CHECK-94.” It
provides an explanation of why the fuel oil truck was condemned.

columns.name: Building Number
columns.description: The building number of the business’s address.

columns.name: Street
columns.description: The street name of the business’s address.

columns.name: City
columns.description: The city where the business is located.

columns.name: State
columns.description: The state where the business is located.

columns.name: Zip
columns.description: The zip code where the business is located.

columns.name: Unit
columns.description: The unit number of the business’s address.

columns.name: Longitude
columns.description: Longitude of business’s address.

columns.name: Latitude
columns.description: Latitude of business’s address.
